OL,5, UK workers are taking more sick days   
OL,6, than at any point in the last decade,  
OL,7, new research suggests.                 
OL,9,FStaff took on average 7.8 sick days in 
OL,10,Fthe past year, up from 5.8 before the  
OL,11,Fpandemic, the Chartered Institute for  
OL,12,FProfessional Development (CIPD) found. 
OL,14,FThe trade group said the rise was a    
OL,15,F"worry" and blamed stress, Covid and   
OL,16,Fthe cost-of-living crisis.             
OL,18,FThese conditions were having "profound 
OL,19,Fimpacts on many people's wellbeing", it
OL,20,Fadded.                                 
